Some of them have up to 14 orphans in their care, offer them a roof to live in and ensure that children go to school every day on time and dressed in their uniforms.
Those who have no one are left under the protection of Khanyisile, a single woman who, like the two cooks who cook every day for more than 200 hungry children, receives a salary from the association.
